      "date": "2017-10-18 19:14:28.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-33vm1 for custom received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/5de3046c-f3a1-473f-aa1a-4b8926f3b693). Ran 4 tests. No failures.",
